	<h1 class="title">QQ 做了《火星救援》表情包，明年还要植入好莱坞大片</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/117425/small/117425.?1433669313" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">王珊珊 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-04 07:47:59 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18488/medium/18488.jpg?1449149868" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


